accessibility.text: My name is Adam. I just get master of ecology degree from Harvard University. I am very enthusiastic about ecology, but I not good at communicate with people. So I decide to go to a private high school because
I want to challenge myself to be a ecology teacher. I hopes I can lead more people to appreciate what we have right now.
